</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#484848><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/bunexplainedmysteries.showUserPublicProfile?gid=westsidemike>westside mike</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(12/1/02 5:51:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   DEATH, GRIM REAPER, ETC ETC</span><hr size=1> OK....THERE IS A MEXICAN VERSION OF DEATH OR THE GRIM REAPER....HE IS CALLED &quot;LA SANTISIMA MUERTE&quot;<br>
 ALL YOU HAVE TO DO IS TYPE THIS INTO A SEARCH ENGINE AND IT SHOULD RETRIEVE SEVERAL RESULTS, SOME IN ENGLISH, BUT MOSTLY SPANISH....<br>
